# Community Domain Rules

## User Profiles
- Comprehensive farmer profiles with farm details
- Public/private profile settings
- Profile verification system
- Skills and expertise showcase
- Location-based networking

## Messaging System
- Real-time chat with Pusher integration
- Group messaging for communities
- File sharing capabilities
- Message moderation and reporting
- Offline message sync

## Events & Networking
- Agricultural events calendar
- Local meetup organization
- Workshop and training announcements
- Event registration and attendance tracking
- Post-event feedback and ratings

## Forums & Discussions
- Category-based discussion forums
- Question and answer system
- Expert verification and badges
- Content moderation tools
- Search and filtering capabilities

## Matchmaking & Collaboration
- Farmer-to-farmer connections
- Expertise-based matching
- Collaborative project creation
- Mentorship program matching
- Business partnership opportunities

## Notifications
- Real-time push notifications
- Email notification preferences
- SMS alerts for critical updates
- In-app notification center
- Notification history and management

